A **step-up SIP calculator** (also called a top-up SIP or increasing SIP calculator) estimates the final corpus when you increase your monthly SIP by a fixed percentage every year. Enter your starting monthly SIP amount, annual step-up percentage, expected return rate, and tenure — the calculator shows the final corpus alongside the equivalent flat SIP corpus so you can see exactly how much extra wealth the annual increases generate.

A 10% annual step-up matches the average salary growth for Indian salaried professionals. Starting with ₹5,000/month and stepping up by 10% every year builds nearly 50% more wealth over 10 years compared to a flat ₹5,000/month SIP, without dramatically increasing the monthly burden.
